name: beachtherapy
description:
Required items 

Sea
Sand
Blue or cloudy sky
Swimwear 

Dosage

For the full effectiveness of treatment, one dip per day should be taken for 7 consecutive days. In case of omission of a dose, go surfing on the last day.

Discontinuation of treatment

Do not discontinue treatment without the knowledge of your doctor.

Adverse reactions

Skin burning, hunger, dryness, sleep.

Indications

Stress, boredom, bad mood.
